thread.title: 'Hands off Syria' protesters yell outside White House

title: 'Hands off Syria' protesters yell outside White House
text:
'Hands off Syria' protesters yell outside White House 12:02am BST - 00:59 
Several dozen protesters chanted anti-war slogans outside the White House on Saturday, a day after President Donald Trump ordered precision strikes in Syria in response to an alleged chemical weapons attack. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
